{"rendered": {"description": {"raw": "Add 3 functions in `Mesh` class:\r\n\r\n* `HasSkeleton`: whether the `Mesh` has a skeletal structure associated with it\r\n* `SkeletonLocalTransforms`: get the local transformations of the mesh skeleton\r\n* `SetSkeletonLocalTransforms`: set the local transformations of the mesh skeleton\r\n\r\nAlso, implemented the above three functions in Ogre\r\n\r\nAn example is also added to `examples/actor_animation`. The outcome is as follows:\r\n\r\n* Colloda animation\r\n\r\n![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/kkkpAkp/images/3559310707-dae_motion.gif)\r\n* BVH animation\r\n\r\n![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/kkkpAkp/images/3670517481-bvh_motion.gif)", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Add 3 functions in <code>Mesh</code> class:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>HasSkeleton</code>: whether the <code>Mesh</code> has a skeletal structure associated with it</li>\n<li><code>SkeletonLocalTransforms</code>: get the local transformations of the mesh skeleton</li>\n<li><code>SetSkeletonLocalTransforms</code>: set the local transformations of the mesh skeleton</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, implemented the above three functions in Ogre</p>\n<p>An example is also added to <code>examples/actor_animation</code>. The outcome is as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Colloda animation</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"data/bitbucket.org/repo/kkkpAkp/images/3559310707-dae_motion.gif\" />\n* BVH animation</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"data/bitbucket.org/repo/kkkpAkp/images/3670517481-bvh_motion.gif\" /></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "title": {"raw": "add animation api for mesh and examples to show the function", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>add animation api for mesh and examples to show the function</p>", "type": "rendered"}}, "type": "pullrequest", "description": "Add 3 functions in `Mesh` class:\r\n\r\n* `HasSkeleton`: whether the `Mesh` has a skeletal structure associated with it\r\n* `SkeletonLocalTransforms`: get the local transformations of the mesh skeleton\r\n* `SetSkeletonLocalTransform